Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.63,0:02:21.98,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快樂才會贏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.09,0:02:24.07,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉　不讓不讓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.18,0:02:26.25,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,縱·橫·斜swinging around
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.39,0:02:30.31,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只在放出悅耳音樂　Girls Go Maniac
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.37,0:02:31.77,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種律動　這種迴響
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.90,0:02:33.88,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想盡情嘗試　一直一直
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:36.85,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配合節奏　Chase Chase 明天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:37.87,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Break Break 夢中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:40.17,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Faith Faith 堅決　Shake Shake 熱烈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.29,0:02:43.60,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉浸得讓人難以忘記　喝彩！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.61,0:22:24.11,EDJ2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's deep deep　心の奥深く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.26,0:22:27.13,EDJ2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何にも響かなかったサンクチュアリに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.23,0:22:31.02,EDJ2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,heat heat　火がついちゃったから戻れない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.50,0:22:35.05,EDJ2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's shock shock　衝撃発信して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.22,0:22:38.19,EDJ2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どこまでも　ねえ一緒に行こうよって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.27,0:22:41.92,EDJ2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,rock rock　音の嵐　津波　誘い合う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.61,0:22:45.59,EDJ2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落としたピック　折れたスティック
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.68,0:22:47.37,EDJ2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全然問題ない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.14,0:22:54.29,EDJ2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同じサウンドの中にいる　それが実は奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.56,0:22:59.82,EDJ2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll sing　歌うよ　感じる　そのまま
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.08,0:23:05.06,EDJ2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どんなに小さくても　世界でひとつの歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.16,0:23:08.08,EDJ2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日死んでも悔やまないってくらい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.24,0:23:10.59,EDJ2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全力で生きたいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.70,0:23:12.73,EDJ2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放て　passionate
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.90,0:23:18.25,EDJ2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私たちの、これがPRECIOUS Heart Beat
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.21,0:23:23.73,EDJ2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌うよ　TREASURE Heart Beat
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.17,0:23:26.22,EDJ2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.61,0:22:24.11,EDC2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's deep deep　深沉心底
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.26,0:22:27.13,EDC2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂靜無聲的聖域中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.23,0:22:31.02,EDC2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,heat heat　激情難以遏制
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.50,0:22:35.05,EDC2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's shock shock　衝擊發信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.22,0:22:38.19,EDC2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論何處都攜手向前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.27,0:22:41.92,EDC2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,rock rock　音之狂風海嘯　為之相魅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.61,0:22:45.59,EDC2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉落的撥片　折斷的鼓棍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.68,0:22:47.37,EDC2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都無法阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.14,0:22:54.29,EDC2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共眠一曲已然奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.56,0:22:59.82,EDC2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll sing　歌唱放飛心聲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.08,0:23:05.06,EDC2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渺小的歌聲　蘊含著世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.16,0:23:08.08,EDC2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日沒有遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.24,0:23:10.59,EDC2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此生奮力前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.70,0:23:12.73,EDC2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綻放吧　passionate
